{"tid":2327164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一隻警犬對武漢肺炎病毒測試呈陽性","createTime":"2020-12-16T01:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T02:05:14.000Z","uid":315191,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b836536f5ef873cd4f566107ed943c79e3ba4b5","tid":2327164,"uid":315191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OM0S69Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOM0S69Z.jpg&h=6edee0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漁護署表示，有關個案涉及一隻警犬隊香港國際機場行動基地的德國牧羊犬，領犬員為確診者。漁護署為狗隻抽取的樣本，對測試呈陽性反應，但牠沒有病徵。警犬已被送往港珠澳大橋香港口岸動物居留所檢疫和獸醫學監察。發言人強調，現時未有證據指出寵物在人類感染新型冠狀病毒中扮演傳播角色，寵物畜養人士不論任何情況，都不應棄養寵物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狗狗咁可愛無辜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n汁 :RTHK"},{"pid":"9c8df25956d091ce703b0fcdc91d859188c77c62","tid":2327164,"uid":387165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50140d71c6e34b9e004cf4a32a74d074682d4052","tid":2327164,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T01:32:04.000Z","msg":"狗都係警犬 一樣抵死"},{"pid":"74eee9efe02157cee594e13a84de8acc519c04c0","tid":2327164,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"建議改稱呼「一隻真警犬」"},{"pid":"4dad164cd2aefaf16a0eeb45539b338313ea6dcd","tid":2327164,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"貓狗會唔會傳俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbe2b93337d44d9d59e36d0decfd13559f74e31","tid":2327164,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"警甴真係累人累物 陀衰家<br />\n俾著係我吞槍死咗去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"}]}